data.name: Clefable
data.description: Channel cosmic power and eclipse the competition with Melee Supporter Clefable in Pokémon UNITE.

data.name: Alolan Ninetales
data.description: Alolan Ninetales uses moves that freeze its opponents in ice, making them unable to move or attack.

data.name: Wigglytuff
data.description: Wigglytuff learns lots of moves that can stop opponents in their tracks, making it well-suited to using teamwork tactics with its allies in battle.

data.name: Machamp
data.description: Machamp is a Pokémon that specializes in melee combat, powered by its strong fighting moves.

data.name: Dodrio
data.description: Prove that three heads are better than one with this nimble Speedster coming to Aeos Island. Dodrio is ready to peck apart the competition in Pokémon UNITE.

data.name: Lapras
data.description: Transport your team to victory with the Ranged Defender Lapras in Pokémon UNITE!

data.name: Snorlax
data.description: Snorlax can take a lot of hits. It’s a dependable Pokémon that can protect its allies from harm.

data.name: Dragonite
data.description: Dragonite is ready to rampage through the competition in Pokémon UNITE as a Melee All-Rounder. Harnessing the power of fire, water, and electricity, Dragonite is a powerhouse that’s ready to stomp its way to victory.

data.name: Mew
data.description: Psych out the competition with this trickster of a Ranged Attacker on Aeos Island. Mew is ready to confound the competition with a plethora of moves in Pokémon UNITE!

data.name: Azumarill
data.description: Add a Melee All-Rounder to your team with a whirlpool-wielding Pokémon that’s ready to play rough with the opposition. Azumarill is ready to tackle any challenge in Pokémon UNITE.

data.name: Espeon
data.description: You don’t need Future Sight to see that Espeon has arrived in Pokémon UNITE. This Ranged Attacker demonstrates the power of mind over matter with some impressive psychic moves.

data.name: Umbreon
data.description: Bask in the moonlight as you eclipse the competition with the Melee Defender Umbreon in Pokémon UNITE.

data.name: Blissey
data.description: Blissey is a Pokémon that excels at supporting its allies with moves that restore HP, cure status conditions, or empower allies!

data.name: Leafeon
data.description: Soak up the sun and channel your solar power with the Melee Speedster Leafeon in Pokémon UNITE.

data.name: Glaceon
data.description: Take the Glacial Stage with this sleet-footed Ranged Attacker, and leave your opponents in the diamond dust. Glaceon is ready to dance and prance with ice crystals in Pokémon UNITE.

data.name: Mamoswine
data.description: Mamoswine charges in with versatile ice attacks that can freeze opponents and leave them unable to move.

data.name: Crustle
data.description: Crustle hinders its opponents using many different moves.

data.name: Zoroark
data.description: Confound the competition with Zoroark’s speed and illusions in Pokémon UNITE.

data.name: Chandelure
data.description: Ignite your next fight on Aeos Island with this fiery Ranged Attacker! Chandelure is ready to set the opposition ablaze in Pokémon UNITE.

data.name: Delphox
data.description: Add a Ranged Attacker to your team with this fireball-flinging Pokémon who’s ready to scorch the opposition. Delphox is ready to burn bright in Pokémon UNITE.

data.name: Talonflame
data.description: Talonflame toys with the opposing team by using its moves to quickly maneuver itself and fly over obstacles.

data.name: Sylveon
data.description: Sylveon attacks opponents from a distance while increasing its stats and restoring its HP.

data.name: Goodra
data.description: Slime your way to the top of Aeos Island with the Melee Defender Goodra in Pokémon UNITE.

data.name: Trevenant
data.description: Add a Melee Defender to your UNITE team with a spectral Pokémon that’s ready to terrify the opposition. Trevenant is ready to unleash sinister fire, good old-fashioned slapping, and terrifying curses in order to win.
